---
const contactEmail = 'sales.reservations@lacasaquecanta.com';
const contactPhone = '+52 (755) 555 7030';
const contactPhoneHref = 'tel:+527555557030';
interface Props {
  lang?: 'en' | 'es';
}
const { lang = 'en' } = Astro.props;
const privacyNav = {
  en: { home: '/', menu: '/a-la-carte-menu/', contact: '/contact/' },
  es: { home: '/es/', menu: '/es/a-la-carte-menu/', contact: '/es/contact/' },
}[lang];
---

<div id="privacy-header" class="privacy-header">
  <div class="header-surface">
    <header class="header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="sr-only">Home</a>
      <nav class="header-nav" aria-label="Privacy page navigation">
        <a href={privacyNav.home}>Home</a>
        <a href={privacyNav.menu}>Menu</a>
        <a href={privacyNav.contact}>Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <nav class="privacy-language-switch" aria-label="Language switcher">
        <a class:list={[lang === 'en' && 'is-active']} href="/privacy-notice/" hreflang="en">EN</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <a class:list={[lang === 'es' && 'is-active']} href="/es/privacy-notice/" hreflang="es-MX">ES</a>
      </nav>
      <a class="book-link" href="https://www.opentable.com/restref/client/?rid=1261543&restref=1261543&lang=en-US&domain=com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Book Now
      </a>
    </header>
  </div>
  <div id="privacy-gradient" class="header-gradient"></div>
</div>

<main class="privacy-main">
  <div class="fixed-watermark" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="watermark-frame">
      <img src="/logo/logo-watermark.webp" alt="" />
      <div class="watermark-fade"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="privacy-copy">
    <h1>Privacy Notice</h1>

    <div class="legal-content">
      <p>
        In "Mar y Cielo" (operated by CASACANTA ZIHUA S.A. de C.V.) we are aware of the importance of
        maintaining the confidentiality of personal and sensitive information of our guests and clients. We are
        committed to protecting your information and privacy in accordance with the Federal Law on Protection of
        Personal Data Held by Private Parties (Mexico), the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) of the
        European Union, and the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) in the United States. Below, we provide
        important information regarding the collection and use of personal data.
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2>1. Data Collection</h2>
        <p>We may collect personal information at any of the contact and interaction points we have with our clients, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Our website, reservation system, and online forms</li>
          <li>Information sent or shared through our social media channels</li>
          <li>Direct interactions at the restaurant or resort</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This information may include:</p>
        <p>
          Contact details (name, address, email, phone number); reservation or stay details; information related
          to product or service purchases; nationality; passport or ID number, place and date of issue; history of
          previous stays; payment and tax information (including RFC or TAX ID); stay preferences; marketing and
          communication preferences; feedback or opinions; information about travel companions; and medical
          information you choose to share to enhance your stay.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Use of Personal and Sensitive Information</h2>
        <p>We use your personal data to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide the requested services</li>
          <li>Improve our services and guest experience</li>
          <li>Ensure our website and services meet your needs</li>
          <li>Process payments, refunds, and inquiries</li>
          <li>Communicate promotions and service updates</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. Data Transfers</h2>
        <p>We may transfer your data to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Medical professionals in case of emergency</li>
          <li>Third-party providers operating our IT infrastructure</li>
          <li>Government or regulatory authorities when legally required</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If you do not object to these transfers, we will assume your consent.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          CASACANTA ZIHUA S.A. de C.V. has implemented physical, technical, and administrative measures to
          protect your data against unauthorized access, alteration, or loss. Our systems use SSL encryption,
          access controls, and secure backups.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. ARCO Rights, GDPR and CCPA</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Request correction of incorrect or outdated data</li>
          <li>Cancel or request deletion of your data when applicable</li>
          <li>Object to the processing of your data</li>
          <li>Request data portability when applicable</li>
          <li>Revoke your consent at any time</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You may exercise these rights by sending your request to:</p>
        <p>
          <a href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a><br />
          <a href={contactPhoneHref}>{contactPhone}</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          We will respond within the periods established by applicable law. If your request is valid, it will be
          fulfilled according to the applicable legal requirements.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Modifications</h2>
        <p>This Privacy Notice may be updated at any time. Changes will be published at:</p>
        <p><a href="https://marycielo.mx">marycielo.mx</a></p>
        <p><strong>Last updated: July 2026</strong></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Data Controller Identity and Address</h2>
        <p><strong>CASACANTA ZIHUA S.A. de C.V.</strong></p>
        <p>
          <strong>Fiscal address:</strong> Montes Urales 720, Floor 1, Office 1-A, Lomas de Chapultepec I Seccion,
          Miguel Hidalgo, 11000, CDMX, Mexico<br />
          <strong>Restaurant and resort address:</strong> Camino Escenico Playa La Ropa S / N, La Ropa Beach,
          40880 Zihuatanejo, Guerrero, Mexico
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<script>
  const header = document.getElementById('privacy-header');
  const gradientOverlay = document.getElementById('privacy-gradient');

  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    const scrolled = window.scrollY;

    if (scrolled > 50) {
      gradientOverlay?.classList.add('is-visible');
      header?.classList.add('has-shadow');
    } else {
      gradientOverlay?.classList.remove('is-visible');
      header?.classList.remove('has-shadow');
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  .sr-only {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
    white-space: nowrap;
    border: 0;
  }

  .privacy-header {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0 0 auto;
    z-index: 50;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .privacy-header.has-shadow .header-surface {
    box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgb(0 0 0 / 12%);
  }

  .header-surface {
    position: relative;
    background: rgb(255 255 255 / 95%);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }

  .header-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    width: min(100%, 1680px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px clamp(24px, 5vw, 72px);
  }

  .header-nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(26px, 4vw, 42px);
    color: #1b252a;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .privacy-language-switch {
    position: absolute;
    left: clamp(24px, 5vw, 72px);
    top: 68px;
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 7px;
    color: #1b252a;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .privacy-language-switch a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    opacity: 0.65;
  }

  .privacy-language-switch a.is-active {
    opacity: 1;
    border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
  }

  .header-nav a,
  .book-link {
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .book-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    min-height: 48px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 1px solid rgb(27 37 42 / 18%);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    color: #1b252a;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .header-gradient {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 100% 0 auto;
    height: 160px;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgb(0 0 0 / 24%), rgb(0 0 0 / 10%), transparent);
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
  }

  .header-gradient.is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .privacy-main {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 128px 0 84px;
    background: #f2eee7;
  }

  .fixed-watermark {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .watermark-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: min(1590px, 151vw);
    height: min(1590px, 151vw);
  }

  .watermark-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    opacity: 0.35;
    filter: grayscale(1) sepia(0.18);
  }

  .watermark-fade {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 0 40%, rgb(242 238 231 / 48%) 70%, #f2eee7 100%);
  }

  .privacy-copy {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: min(890px, calc(100% - 48px));
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    color: #173a36;
    font-family: var(--title-font);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4.2rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.05;
    text-transform: none;
  }

  .legal-content {
    color: rgb(27 37 42 / 80%);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.72;
  }

  .legal-content section {
    margin-top: 42px;
  }

  .legal-content h2 {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: #173a36;
    font-family: var(--title-font);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-transform: none;
  }

  .legal-content p {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
  }

  .legal-content ul {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    padding-left: 28px;
  }

  .legal-content li {
    margin: 0 0 7px;
  }

  .legal-content a {
    color: #173a36;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .header-inner {
      padding: 16px 22px;
    }

    .header-nav {
      gap: 18px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .privacy-language-switch {
      top: 58px;
      left: 22px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .book-link {
      min-height: 42px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .privacy-main {
      padding-top: 108px;
    }

    .watermark-frame {
      width: 159vw;
      height: 159vw;
    }

    .watermark-frame img {
      opacity: 0.35;
    }

    .privacy-copy {
      width: min(100% - 36px, 890px);
    }

    .legal-content {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  }
</style>
